  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK117">
<l>keṭuvāka vaiyā tulaka naṭuvāka</l>
<l>naṉṟikkaṭ ṭaṅkiyāṉ ṟāḻvu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The world does not reckon it ruin—the low rank</l>
<l>of one who has stayed in virtue's midst.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
